<subSubSection pageId="8" pageNumber="7" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="8.[192,1441,1601,1690]" pageId="8" pageNumber="7">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[192,347,1601,1625]" pageId="8" pageNumber="7">Comments.</emphasis>
While the morphological characters appear consistent, genetic sequencing may clarify the status and relationship of western vs. southeastern populations of this species and related borers of the genus.
</paragraph>
